00:26:11,404 --> 00:26:13,072
Es el único lugar adonde mirar.

389
00:26:14,156 --> 00:26:15,157
Espera.

390
00:26:17,910 --> 00:26:19,036
Solo...

391
00:26:19,537 --> 00:26:21,664
Ten cuidado, ¿sí?

392
00:26:24,417 --> 00:26:26,043
Heather, es ahora o nunca.

393
00:27:03,664 --> 00:27:07,126
