441
00:30:22,488 --> 00:30:25,115
¡Adelante!

442
00:30:26,909 --> 00:30:28,077
¡Es un profesional!

443
00:30:36,877 --> 00:30:37,753
¡Cielos!

444
00:30:44,093 --> 00:30:45,094
Dios mío.

445
00:31:19,044 --> 00:31:20,129
