455
00:32:25,152 --> 00:32:27,488
De rodillas. Levanten las manos.

456
00:32:30,824 --> 00:32:31,659
¡Heather!

457
00:32:34,787 --> 00:32:36,121
-¿Estás bien?
-Sí.

458
00:32:36,872 --> 00:32:37,956
Por aquí.

459
00:32:40,501 --> 00:32:41,418
¡Quietos!

460
00:32:47,716 --> 00:32:48,926
-Mi tobillo.
-Vamos.

461
00:32:53,847 --> 00:32:56,725
